input: What is ICCT colleges?
output: ICCT Colleges Foundation Inc. is a tertiary education provider with campuses located in the Province of Rizal, Philippines. In Rizal, it has campuses in the municipality of Cainta, Sumulong (Cainta), San Mateo, Cogeo, Antipolo, Taytay, Binangonan, and Angono. Course offerings include Arts & Sciences, Business, Computer, Criminology, Education, Engineering, Health Sciences, Hospitality & Tourism Management, Short Term/Certificate Programs, And SENIOR HIGH SCHOOL (Grade 11 & 12).
